                              rubricated. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#78v">f. 78v</locus>
                           <desc>: Prayer to the Trinity and St Mary. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
